data.meta_description: Is Woody Allen dead or alive? Find out at the Dead or Alive Data Base. This reference site helps you keep track of which famous people are alive and which ones have died.
data.text:
Woody Allen

Alive

Born: 12/1/1935 in New York City, New York, USA

Age: 88

Full name: Allan Stewart Konigsberg

Noted For: film director; writes and stars in most of his films, films include What's New, Pussycat (writer, 1965), Sleeper (1973), Annie Hall (1977), A Midsummer Night's Sex Comedy (1982), Crimes and Misdemeanors (1989), Hollywood Ending (2002). Won Academy awards for Annie Hall (Best director, 1978), Hannah and Her Sisters (Best screenplay, 1987). Lover and performing partner of actress Mia Farrow (1982-95).
